619
00:25:49,300 --> 00:25:50,640
to face Wan'er.

620
00:25:51,190 --> 00:25:52,330
That's right.

621
00:25:52,910 --> 00:25:54,870
The point is, you should

622
00:25:54,870 --> 00:25:57,010
