623
00:26:04,150 --> 00:26:05,060
Thank you, Auntie.

624
00:26:05,060 --> 00:26:06,200
You look gorgeous today.

625
00:26:16,470 --> 00:26:18,490
Aji needs me, at last.

626
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:21,200
Madam,

627
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,250
