628
00:26:25,260 --> 00:26:26,730
What is wrong?

629
00:26:27,100 --> 00:26:28,600
He calls her Wan'er.

630
00:26:30,190 --> 00:26:31,130
Wan'er...

631
00:26:31,540 --> 00:26:32,490
