751
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:10,630
We never said that.

752
00:32:10,630 --> 00:32:11,570
Never.

753
00:32:13,470 --> 00:32:15,050
I'll let you guys talk.

754
00:32:17,870 --> 00:32:18,870
You...

755
