756
00:32:19,990 --> 00:32:20,930
Nothing.

757
00:32:21,710 --> 00:32:23,100
Come on, Wanqing.

758
00:32:23,100 --> 00:32:24,020
Sit wherever you want.

759
00:32:24,020 --> 00:32:24,960
Oh, Guiwei.

760
00:32:25,230 --> 00:32:26,780
We asked you to think of the last step

761
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:28,360
