865
00:36:11,470 --> 00:36:12,750
- No, Sixi.
- Don't touch me.

866
00:36:12,750 --> 00:36:14,060
We have things to do. Bye.

867
00:36:14,060 --> 00:36:15,000
Eat the soup while it's hot.

868
00:36:15,180 --> 00:36:16,750
Contact us after you wake up tomorrow.

